N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 153.2 - Registration of certain service providers

State Regulations

Every political consultant shall, within ten days of the
close of the applicable reporting period, unless otherwise directed by the

Department, file with the Department the registration form prescribed by this
